{"word":"G2722 - κατέχω - katéchō - kat-ekh'-o - Have","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατέχω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katéchō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ekh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Have</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கட்டிக்கொள், நிறுத்திக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"to hold back, detain, retain"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G2192 - ἔχω - échō - ekh'-o/2192\">G2192</a>; to <i>hold down</i> (<i>fast</i>), in various applications (literally or figuratively): - have, hold (fast), keep (in memory), let, X make toward, possess, retain, seize on, stay, take, withhold.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1777/1777\">G1777</a>, <a href=\"#/G2192/2192\">G2192</a>, <a href=\"#/G2722/2722\">G2722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3348/3348\">G3348</a>, <a href=\"#/G3353/3353\">G3353</a>, <a href=\"#/G472/472\">G472</a>, <a href=\"#/G568/568\">G568</a>"}]}